context: <user>  Can you help me with train schedules? <system>  I certainly can. What did you have in mind? <user>  I am looking for trains that depart from cambridge and go to broxbourne. <system>  We've got several trains going that route. Is there a particular day or time you need? <user>  I need to go on Friday. <system>  What time will you be departing from cambridge? Also what time do you need to arrive in broxbourne by? <user>  I just need to arrive by 18:30, the departure time doesn't matter. <system>  I have several that arrive before 18:30. I have one that arrives at 16:01, 17:01, and 18:01. They all leave an hour before arrival time and are 17.90 pounds.<user>  Can you book the train that will arrive at 18:01 and I need 4 tickets. <system>  Your booking was successful and the total fee is 71.59 GBP, which is payable at the station. Your reference number is D3L643YZ .<user>  Thanks. I also need a guesthouse to stay in in the north. <system>  How about the acorn guest house?<user>  Does it offer free wifi? I'd also like it to have 4 stars. <system>  Yes, it fits all those needs.<user>  Great. Please book it for 2 nights starting on Wednesday. <system>  How many people will be staying?<user>  There will be a party of four. <system>  Booking was successful. Reference number is : 8P7QUDHW .<user>  thanks for helping. <system>  You're welcome! Can I help you with anything else?<user>  No that was all thank you so much. <system>
